commit.message: Effort to make picture more reliable.
Fixed display of menu choices to be complete and orderly.
Updated gesture detection so that it returns an integer value
Added a method to detect how many fingers are being held up in a photo
Changed menu.html file so that the form is only submitted once
Add notivize message send on conclusion of taking input.
Added alterations to raw photos to match data set.
Renamed class name and renamed file to class name.
Made new route where list of inputs may be taken from the user and inputs are displayed at end.
Flask server which serves output of imported gesture detection method with the input of a webcam image taken upon a get request to the server.
Added readme with brief description of project idea.
